snippet.title: 【Comedy Movie】🎄Crazy New Year’s EVE🎊│Amber Kuo, Jam Hsiao, Zhao Liying│Fresh Drama+
snippet.description:
#CrazyNewYearsEVE #Comedy #Romance #Christmas

❣Welcome to follow our Facebook→ https://www.facebook.com/FreshDramaTV
❣Click to subscribe our Channel→ https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9KQJM5HxBAW5RnRelxhqNw?sub_confirmation=1

Synopsis:
When preparing for the 100th wedding, Jiayi, an seasoned wedding planner, feels that she has the impulse to get married, but her boyfriend who witnessed his parents' marriage failure is afraid of marriage.
Retired gymnast Nana goes into labor on New Year's Eve. But her husband, superstar Jing Ming, needs to participate in the countdown to the new year on TV. He must make a choice between work and wife.
After catching the suspect, the workaholic cop Zhong Wei was moved by the story of the suspect and his grandmother, which awakened his longing for family.

Subtitles: English [CC]

Audio languages: English

Director: Eva Jin, Pan Anzi, Zhang Jiarui

Cast:
Amber Kuo as Jia Yi
Rhydian Vaughan as Willy
Zhao Li Ying as Li Nana
Jam Hsiao as Xiao Jing Ming
Xia Yu as Zhong Wei
Mei Ting as Zhang Wei Wei
Lam Ka Tung as Zhang Jia Lun
